data.title: Danilo Barthel Biography
data.meta_description: Read all about Danilo Barthel with TV Guide's exclusive biography including their list of awards, celeb facts and more at TV Guide.
data.text:
Fast Facts

•Barthel began his career with hometown club USC Heidelberg in 2008

•During the 2013/14 season, he played 34 league games for Frankfurt, averaging 11

3 points, 4

9 rebounds and 1

4 assists in 28

1 minutes per game

• He made his debut for the Germany national basketball team on 27 July 2014 in a game against Finland

• He signed a two year deal with Bayern Munich on July 6 2016

•He won his first BBL Championship with Bayern after defeating Alba Berlin 3-2 in the finals on June 17 2018

He was named the Finals MVP after the decisive game five
